    <title>PostgreSQL - Import / export CSV</title>
    <link>https://l-lin.github.io/2020-04-15-psql-import_export_csv/</link>
    <pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2020 11:06:08 &#43;0200</pubDate>
    <author>Author</author>
    <guid>https://l-lin.github.io/2020-04-15-psql-import_export_csv/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="https://www.virtual-dba.com/media/postgresql-database-services-remote-dba.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><p>Export:</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"><span class="err">\</span><span class="k">copy</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="k">SELECT</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="k">FROM</span> <span class="n">your_table</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">TO</span> <span class="s1">&#39;/tmp/your_table.csv&#39;</span> <span class="n">CSV</span> <span class="n">HEADER</span> <span class="k">FORCE</span> <span class="n">QUOTE</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>Import:</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre class="chroma"><code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"><span class="err">\</span><span class="k">copy</span> <span class="n">your_table</span> <span class="k">FROM</span> <span class="s1">&#39;/tmp/your_table.csv&#39;</span> <span class="n">CSV</span> <span class="n">HEADER</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div>]]></description>
</item><item>
    <title>Remove idle transactions</title>
